<title type="html"><![CDATA[1/14.(Thu.)5 Common types of water leakages and solutions/21 Tiny Inconveniences That Actually Drive You Crazy (William)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=464&amp;p=482#p482"><![CDATA[
1/14.(Thu.)5 Common types of water leakages and solutions/21 Tiny Little Inconveniences That Actually Drive You Crazy (Host: William)<br /><br />Place: 丹堤咖啡, 台北市延平南路107號2樓 (MRT 西門站4號出口)<br />Agenda:<br />6:30-7:15 pm Free talk<br />7:15-7:50 pm Session 1 discussion<br />7:50-8:15 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:15-8:45 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:45-9:00 pm Presentation<br /><br />Article1:<br /><br /><a href="https://sghomeneeds.com/articles/water-leakages-and-solution" class="postlink">https://sghomeneeds.com/articles/water-leakages-and-solution</a><br /><br />5 Common types of water leakages and solutions<br /><br />1. Have you ever experienced a drip water coming from the ceiling above you ? Has the leakage been fixed ? Who will pay the repair expense ?<br />2. How do you find the competent contractor and plumber to repair the leakage ?<br />3. Have you ever used DIY to repair the leakages ? Was it difficult ?<br />4. If you want to buy a house. How do you choose the good construction building ?<br /><br />Article2:<br /><br /><a href="https://www.buzzfeed.com/stephenlaconte/little-things-that-make-people-rage" class="postlink">https://www.buzzfeed.com/stephenlaconte/little-things-that-make-people-rage</a><br /><br />What are the little things in day life that drive you crazy ?<br />What annoys you the most in the following :<br /><br />1. Making loud personal call in your office.<br />2. This woman put her bare feet on the back of this man's chair.<br />3. Drivers who don't signal when changing lanes. It takes a second.<br />4. When two people in a store stop, carts side by side, and block the entire aisle to have a conversation.<br />5. The lavatory has a sign to indicate that it's occupied . There are always people trying to open the door just to make sure that it's really in use.<br /><br />----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Fri Jan 08, 2021 10:14 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
